<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910621-0192</DOCNO><DOCID>910621-0192.</DOCID><HL>   Arkla Exploration Buys Hunter</HL><DATE>06/21/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   ARK ALG</CO><MS>ENERGY (ENE)</MS><IN>OIL DRILLING AND EXPLORATION (DRL)OIL EQUIPMENT AND SERVICES (OIE)PETROLEUM (PET)TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)</IN><NS>ACQUISITIONS andamp; MERGERS, TAKEOVERS, BOARD BATTLES (TNM)</NS><RE>LOUISIANA (LA)NORTH AMERICA (NME)UNITED STATES (US)</RE><LP>   SHREVEPORT, La. -- Arkla Exploration Co. said it acquiredclosely held Hunter Co., an oil and gas company, in a cashand stock transaction valued at $20 million.   Arkla, an oil and gas exploration company, said Hunter isa Shreveport, La., company with holdings in the CarthageField of East Texas. Arkla said the acquisition will addabout 15 billion cubic feet of natural gas reserves to itsholdings.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>